    "description": "<p>Established in 1981, Yeakin Plastic Industry (YPI) is a leading manufacturer of precision plastic components.<br>\nOur core capabilities include precision mould making, injection moulding, insert moulding and component sub-assembly.<br>\nYPI Group has grown into an industry leader, delivering fully integrated manufacturing solutions across diverse sectors such as medical, automotive, high-end consumer electronics and other advanced industries.<br>\nHeadquartered in Singapore, the Group operates three production bases—in Singapore, Suzhou (China) and Batam (Indonesia). Today, YPI employs nearly 2,000 people across three countries, with a combined gross floor area of 57,000 m².<br>\nWe are proud to be certified to international standards, including ISO/TS 16949, ISO 9001, ISO 13485 and ISO 14001, demonstrating our commitment to quality, innovation and sustainability.<br>\n</p>",
